&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. Variant of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-381&quot; title=&quot;Fail fast if configure detects C++ problems&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-381&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-381&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, will not address within this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. Updated options parser with usage message with errors and only display help when asked for it. &lt;/p&gt;
